more motion sensors

07:55.642 --> 07:57.882
and those night vision cameras.

07:58.242 --> 08:00.409
You around tomorrow to help
set 'em up?

08:00.445 --> 08:02.414
Mm-hmm.

08:03.049 --> 08:05.265
