take care of.

08:19.867 --> 08:22.568
What? You got a shift
at chili's?

08:23.574 --> 08:25.075
Baby, can you do me a favor?

08:25.116 --> 08:26.613
Do you think you and deran
can go pick up

08:26.637 --> 08:28.195
the sliding doors for me?

08:28.278 --> 08:31.054
- Yeah, I'll talk to him.
- Thank you, baby.

08:33.216 --> 08:35.136
All right, I gotta go.
You need a ride to school?

08:35.222 --> 08:36.773
Sure.

08:46.669 --> 08:48.729
Carrying?

08:50.190 --> 08:51.916
I won't get caught off guard
again.

08:52.018 --> 08:54.346
Then you should learn to make
your own loads.

08:54.382 --> 08:56.088
It's harder to trace.

08:56.139 --> 08:57.622
You want me to teach you?

08:57.646 --> 08:58.799
Yeah, sure.

08:58.858 --> 09:01.033
After school.

09:01.592 --> 09:03.674
Cool.

09:33.980 --> 09:35.971
You're like a college kid.

09:36.113 --> 09:37.656
All pent up, hungry.

09:43.461 --> 09:45.026
Hell's that supposed to mean?

09:45.144 --> 09:48.299
It's called a compliment.
It means you're good in bed.

