to me, did I freak out?

10:22.272 --> 10:24.396
Did I call the cops?

10:24.778 --> 10:26.240
You can trust me.

10:26.392 --> 10:27.568
I trust you.

10:27.652 --> 10:31.076
Okay, prove it.

10:31.663 --> 10:33.146
I'm setting up a job.

10:33.234 --> 10:35.935
