10:36.208 --> 10:37.513
We're gonna be pirates.

10:37.633 --> 10:39.865
- Huh?
- We're gonna rob a boat.

10:39.930 --> 10:41.787
Oh, that is so cool!

10:41.944 --> 10:44.873
Yeah.
It is.

10:45.270 --> 10:47.162
Okay, what's my part in it?

10:47.356 --> 10:50.490
