10:54.560 --> 10:55.960
You know,
when I first met you,

10:56.025 --> 10:57.692
I thought you were
a total asshole.

10:58.114 --> 10:59.860
Well,
the feeling was mutual.

11:00.209 --> 11:01.907
I wasn't the one talkin'.

11:02.186 --> 11:03.642
Well, you didn't have to be.

11:03.878 --> 11:05.274
You walked in,

11:05.402 --> 11:07.168
thought you were too cool
to be there.

11:07.259 --> 11:10.001
- Mm-hmm.
- It's just my type.

11:10.573 --> 11:12.095
So I'm a type?

11:12.258 --> 11:14.224
Oh, everybody's a type.

11:17.212 --> 11:20.228
Jesus.
Dude, are you kidding me?

11:20.383 --> 11:21.923
You gotta get your shit
together here.

11:22.051 --> 11:23.634
What?

11:24.106 --> 11:26.626
That's a very carefully
designed system.

11:26.807 --> 11:28.656
Look, I've sold
a lot of properties

11:28.719 --> 11:30.532
to first-time business owners
who've bellied up,

11:30.556 --> 11:32.008
let the little things
overwhelm them.

11:32.060 --> 11:33.648
- It's always the little things.
- Yeah.

11:33.655 --> 11:35.485
The big stuff...
Floods, earthquakes...

11:35.556 --> 11:36.415
You got insurance for that.

11:38.128 --> 11:40.642
You do have insurance for that,
right?

11:42.493 --> 11:44.790
Yeah, I'm shoppin' around.

11:45.641 --> 11:47.453
Okay. Uh...

11:48.438 --> 11:50.103
This is my insurance guy.

11:50.470 --> 11:52.243
And a bookkeeper,

11:52.459 --> 11:54.923
