12:04.670 --> 12:06.813
Why'd you think
I came here last night?

12:06.996 --> 12:08.657
To get you to pay.

12:08.841 --> 12:10.477
Well, that's funny 'cause
I thought, you know,

12:10.501 --> 12:12.539
