13:17.248 --> 13:20.479
- Thanks.
- Yeah.

13:21.132 --> 13:24.188
Um...

13:26.691 --> 13:29.494
So...

13:29.665 --> 13:30.806
I'm sorry. You guys...

13:30.877 --> 13:33.284
Do you guys mind if we pick this
up on Thursday?

13:33.441 --> 13:34.812
Yeah?

13:36.722 --> 13:39.617
Thank you so much.
What'd they say?

13:41.224 --> 13:43.159
Just a sec.

13:43.331 --> 13:44.577
You okay?

13:44.698 --> 13:46.225
Not really.

13:46.370 --> 13:47.722
They were looking for Leon.

13:47.784 --> 13:49.206
They've been trying
to reach him.

13:49.331 --> 13:51.761
There's no way Leon would steal
from the church.

13:51.886 --> 13:54.564
Since he got out, this place has
been everything to him.

13:54.589 --> 13:55.963
You should call him
and tell him

13:55.995 --> 13:58.120
the worst thing he could do
is avoid them.

13:58.183 --> 14:00.636
Okay. Yeah. Um...

14:07.040 --> 14:09.261
Straight to voice mail.

14:10.195 --> 14:14.089
I know where he works.
Will you come, talk to him?

14:14.406 --> 14:18.308
Mm, no, I don't think
that's a good idea.

14:18.441 --> 14:22.441
If... if Leon's not calling
them back, he's scared.

14:22.875 --> 14:25.527
Okay,
you've done time.

14:25.653 --> 14:28.855
