14:53.304 --> 14:54.511
He should have 'em.

14:54.605 --> 14:57.464
Huh? Listen to... Eric.

14:57.580 --> 14:59.191
Come on, on the couch.

14:59.323 --> 15:00.339
Let's go.

15:00.370 --> 15:01.722
All right.

15:02.000 --> 15:03.073
I'll do it.

15:03.192 --> 15:04.760
