15:07.448 --> 15:08.706
All right, let's go.

15:08.877 --> 15:11.077
Nah, I'm... I'm cool, man.

15:11.282 --> 15:12.972
You sure?

15:13.290 --> 15:16.081
Yeah, whatever, man.

15:16.523 --> 15:18.128
All right.

15:18.770 --> 15:21.050
I owe you one. Thank you.

15:21.386 --> 15:23.464
- Eric.
- Dana.

15:23.550 --> 15:27.437
- Nice to meet you, Dana.
- Nice to meet you, Eric.

15:35.208 --> 15:36.589
Making loads?

15:36.845 --> 15:39.120
J wants to learn.

15:39.469 --> 15:40.870
What's in the box?

15:41.011 --> 15:42.753
You know,
it's the new motion sensors.

15:42.823 --> 15:44.711
Gotta make sure they're
compatible with the alarm.

15:46.014 --> 15:48.855
Craig and deran still bitching
about not getting paid

15:48.927 --> 15:50.589
to save their mother?

15:50.843 --> 15:55.120
Just throw 'em 5 grand, or I'll
never hear the end of it.

15:56.707 --> 15:58.878
I'm gonna need
the $200,000 back.

15:58.931 --> 16:00.720
I'm not sure the other guys
would be too cool

16:00.745 --> 16:02.479
knowing you used
their money for a hit.

16:02.548 --> 16:05.307
Okay.

16:06.111 --> 16:07.620
Tomorrow?

16:07.904 --> 16:09.448
Yeah, I'll go to the bank.

16:09.532 --> 16:11.792
Use credit if I have to.

16:12.007 --> 16:13.307
Good.

16:13.517 --> 16:14.885
- Baz?
- Yeah?

16:14.981 --> 16:17.573
You know what
I was thinking earlier?

16:18.000 --> 16:20.500
Do you remember
when pope was 13

16:20.659 --> 16:24.518
and he decided that the cops
had tapped all our phones lines,

16:24.630 --> 16:26.784
ripped every phone
out of the wall?

16:26.999 --> 16:30.729
And then he ran out back and
climbed up the telephone pole?

16:30.754 --> 16:33.385
